    <summary>
      Created OperationFeedback component for real-time AI processing status:

      1. COMPONENT STRUCTURE:
         - Spinner or Checkmark icon
         - Status text (main message)
         - Step text (current operation)
         - Operation count badge

      2. STATE INTEGRATION:
         - Reads isStreaming and streamingState from aiAssistantStore
         - Auto-detects visibility based on streaming state
         - Shows "Complete!" briefly after streaming ends

      3. VISUAL STATES:
         - Active (streaming): Brand background, brand border
         - Complete: Green background, green border, checkmark
         - Default: Neutral background

      4. CONFIGURABLE:
         - visible: Override auto-visibility
         - statusText: Custom main text
         - stepText: Custom operation text
         - showBadge: Toggle operation count badge
         - showCompleteState: Toggle completion animation
         - completeDuration: Duration to show complete state (ms)
         - compact: Single-line mode

      5. STYLING (ADR-021 COMPLIANT):
         - All colors use Fluent tokens
         - tokens.colorBrandBackground2 for active state
         - tokens.colorPaletteGreenBackground1 for complete
         - Responsive with overflow handling

      6. ACCESSIBILITY:
         - role="status" for live region
         - aria-live="polite" for updates
         - aria-label for context

      7. FILES MODIFIED:
         - components/AiAssistant/OperationFeedback.tsx (175 lines)
         - components/AiAssistant/index.ts (added export)

